Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:38.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:46.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:49.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:03:00.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:03.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that \Nthe prize for a fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,event was the Flare-Flare \NFruit, he decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first round is a battle royal\Nwhere only one can win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burgess from the Blackbeard Pirates won\Nthe match of Block A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the battle of Block B has begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competitors led by Dagama, the tactician,\Nare protecting Elizabello II,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the king of Prodence Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is he going to throw\Nthe devastating King Punch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Atrocious"! "Evil"!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the words only fitting to this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the top contender\Nto beat Elizabello II after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime,\Nthe Jiaokungdo martial artist - Blue Gilly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the mysterious gladiator - Ricky,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe two strong men are fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4000 Brick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?!\NHack is the one who collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of monster are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Deadly Blow!\NThe Astonishing King Punch!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hack got defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even reach Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Bartolomeo do to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I was rooting for Hack!\NThat chicken head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyats-{\i1}san{\i0}, you have to be fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see a clear winner yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B Block - 24 competitors remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be over soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's got a wound or two now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful competitors are getting eliminated\None after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following Hack's defeat,\Nthe unknown gladiator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ricky, also got taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Gilly is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Blue Gilly-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you can cut
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with such a blunt sword, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I can't fight aging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand all this cheering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand you, Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't that many men left\Nthanks to Dagama's tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the competitors are gone\Nexcept for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe I'm still here.\NI'm glad that I allied with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Dagama gives us the cue,\Nwe'll disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll fight amongst ourselves\Nuntil one of us wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take down as many \Nenemies as possible for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Gilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Take care of Blue Gilly\Nwhile we're fighting together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:08:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a fine job, you stupid dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you haven't given us the cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he... Hey, Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I've been told to hunt you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you plotting together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get rid of us from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pay you later!\NYour job is done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors who can't use their brains
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just end up as someone's \Npuppets on a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you, Longfeet man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now you turned your back to me,\Nyou're dead, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue Gilly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We of the Prodence Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:15.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,will win the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nat any cost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me, Blue Gilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama the tactician got eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Way to go, Longfeet guy!\N--Blue Gilly-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe people would trust a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dubious guy like him\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go, Bellamy!\N--Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our man - Bellamy is beginning to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His target is the "most annoying pirate\Nwho should just go away"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy who went in for the attack\Nis down on the floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Bartolomeo do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy delivered an attack\Nand got hurt like Hack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...struggling like this right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Death Knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our man - Bellamy is worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Devil Fruit did he eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no interest in the Flare-Flare Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have my own reason to win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get on board Doflamingo's \Nship to ride through the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"wild wave" that will come sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done picking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what are you gonna do, Elizabello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is more helpless than a king\Nwithout his court.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody was dying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who had been guarding you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhave turned against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything \Nwithout Dagama, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagama did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is throw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the ones who were protected
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while we were in that battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because nothing is more dangerous \Nthan an exposed blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, you punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report about \Nthe king of Prodence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said he destroyed an
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enemy country's fort\Nwith a single punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He must've used some kind of weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they say it could take down\Neven the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, he's gonna throw a punch that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will destroy this part of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He can't throw such a destructive punch\Nat a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a restlessness in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king who kept quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the battle formation is\Nnow on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Prodence Kingdom will win\Nthe Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?\NWhat do you wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, in order to \Ndestroy the SMILE factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta beat up someone in the Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! I've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I have no time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have nothing to talk about, I'm gonna go now!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep talking about this radical plan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why do you want to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you know things\Nthat ordinary people don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your true purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, we better go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, he really did destroy the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent!\NWhat's this?! Get it off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Don't underestimate \Nthe power of my spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill Elizabello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in the Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How powerful was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone in the \Nring could survive that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabello II wiped out all of his enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a single punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a hell of a punch!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! Blue Gilly!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all other potential \Nwinners have been eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle royal of Block B - 138 \Ncompetitors - the winner is from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Prodence Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Somebody's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see? Right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience in that direction \Ndidn't get blown away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecause of his defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can create barriers\Nby crossing their fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common knowledge!\NEven kids know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a barrier human who ate \Nthe Barrier-Barrier Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fighting King" - Elizabello \NII got knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of Block B is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go away!\N--Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That strange guy won.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will dedicate the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nto that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're plotting to destroy the factory, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! My friends and I have been\Ncarrying out preparations for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where it is!\NI'll destroy it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we want to save the \Nworkers in the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The workers in the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan could lead to \Nthe fall of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's a big project!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the nerve and are \Ndetermined to go against Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:23:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you everything\Nabout this tragic kingdom - Dressrosa!
